title.rendered: Tyra Banks Welcomes Kardashian Klan on Stage

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

In what is sure to be the world’s most annoying talk show episode, the Kardashian sisters will appear on The Tyra Banks show on September 23.

The stage doesn’t seem big enough for this quartert of attention mongers, as Tyra is known as much for her self-serving ways as her beauty, while Kim Kardashian is known to do anyone to stay in the spotlight (see J, Ray).

Khloe and Kourtney Kardashian? They’re known for spelling their first names in a ridiculous fashion.

We feel horrible for anyone in the audience during this taping.
